Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.49,0:21:12.48,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}縱使深陷天大的謊言中
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.48,0:21:16.60,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想愛下去
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.87,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}夜色滿溢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.13,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}配合著步伐
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.13,0:21:27.95,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}時鐘停擺 淡淡的詛咒纏繞著我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.95,0:21:32.46,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}你的反應總是在逃避
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.98,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}如果只是想重來而已
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.98,0:21:41.30,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}那你這樣吊著我又是何必
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.30,0:21:45.84,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我想知道我的心該放在哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.84,0:21:50.35,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}遲早都會迎來結束
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.35,0:21:53.17,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我早就清清楚楚
